"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1931758-Imane-Khelif-Olympics-fight-gender-boxing-row\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Imane Khelif has guaranteed herself anOlympicmedal in Paris as the Algerian boxer claimed a unanimous points victory over Luca Anna Hamori in the women's 66kg category as the gender row goes on in the background.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 214, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999158717, \"rank\": 8.401785082153696e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 69, \"end\": 77, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999217238692959, \"rank\": 7.312721460303342e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 129, \"end\": 133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"score\": 0.9993625007879444, \"rank\": 0.0006244191218499832, \"text\": \"Anna\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anna_Freud\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, Khelif wasdisqualified from the women's World Championships in New Delhi for failing a gender eligibility test.\", \"from\": 216, \"to\": 338, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9997492423536588, \"rank\": 0.0002508198851590043, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting was also banned for failing to meet the gender eligibility criteria of the International Boxing Association (IBA), though both have been cleared to compete in Paris.\", \"from\": 339, \"to\": 525, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 339, \"end\": 345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9997591791871158, \"rank\": 0.00023650443277755333, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 467, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.1373731299707382e-28, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.5750889219630199, \"rank\": 0.7388615249640778, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 519, \"end\": 524, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999158717, \"rank\": 8.401785082153696e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif will next face Thailand's Janjaem Suwannapheng in the semi-finals, two days afterAngela Carini quit just 46 seconds into their last 16 boutwith Khelif following two significant punches from the Algerian.\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 549, \"end\": 557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"score\": 0.8319232307275878, \"rank\": 0.2020336664475252, \"text\": \"Thailand\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thailand\"}, {\"begin\": 622, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9616270791009309, \"rank\": 0.03990416007707136, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999217238692959, \"rank\": 7.312721460303342e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 739, \"to\": 783, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 853, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 854, \"to\": 870, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The first round against Hamori saw both boxers hit and get hit.\", \"from\": 872, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerian landed a powerful one-two but as the first three minutes went on the more Hamori grew into the contest, Khelif however edged the scorecards.\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999217238692959, \"rank\": 7.312721460303342e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An entertaining second saw plenty of to and fro, with Khelif cheered on by a large Algerian contingent inside the venue, though the 25-year-old was well on top and Hamori required a knock-out in the third to snatch victory and the promise of an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999217238692959, \"rank\": 7.312721460303342e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That knock-out would not come, however, as Khelif stood firm and eventually won unanimously on points.\", \"from\": 1352, \"to\": 1454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her victory did not come with any significant drama reminiscent of the furore of Khelif's previous win, with Hamori touching gloves following the verdict in a mark of respect to her opponent.\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1647, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1758, \"end\": 1763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999158717, \"rank\": 8.401785082153696e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1869, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1839, \"end\": 1851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9994765198657469, \"rank\": 0.0005237543084921588, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1870, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IBA has not specified why Khelif or Lin failed their gender eligibility tests in 2023, but clarified that the pair did not undergo testosterone examinations.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2087, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1930, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.5750889219630199, \"rank\": 0.7388615249640778, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Neither boxer identifies as transgender or intersex.\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On the morning of Khelif's fight with Hamori, her fatherAmar felt compelled to share an official document confirming that his daughter was born female.\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He then launched a stinging attack on the criticism that Khelif has faced over the past few days, insisting: \\\"The attacks against her are immoral, it is not fair.\", \"from\": 2295, \"to\": 2457, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Imane is a little girl that has loved sport since she was six-years-old, she used to play football.\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2559, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These critics and rumours aim to destabilise Imane, they do not want her to be the champion of the world.\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I tell her prove them wrong in the ring and I hope that she will honour Algeria and Arabic countries and win the gold medal.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2740, \"end\": 2747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999957662906618, \"rank\": 3.1545489891703355e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2752, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabic\", \"score\": 0.6947477316216433, \"rank\": 0.4388511870166204, \"text\": \"Arabic\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arabic\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She is our role model, and we want to be like her and honour Algeria and Tiaret.\\\"\", \"from\": 2793, \"to\": 2874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2854, \"end\": 2861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999957662906618, \"rank\": 3.1545489891703355e-06, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 2866, \"end\": 2872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\", \"score\": 0.99999999990996, \"rank\": 8.985452179659704e-11, \"text\": \"Tiaret\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tiaret\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini, who quit after 46 seconds against Khelif and kickstarted the fury towards her opponent earlier in the week,has since apologised for not shaking the Algerian's handand for her post-fight comments.\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 3081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2878, \"end\": 2884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9616270791009309, \"rank\": 0.03990416007707136, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q378622\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Piero_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 3034, \"end\": 3042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9999217238692959, \"rank\": 7.312721460303342e-05, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All this controversy makes me sad,\\\" the Italian claimed.\", \"from\": 3083, \"to\": 3140, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3124, \"end\": 3131, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9492581498054223, \"rank\": 0.051853714507484515, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am sorry for my opponent, too.\", \"from\": 3141, \"to\": 3174, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 If the IOC said she can fight, I respect that decision.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3184, \"end\": 3187, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.620193080865369e-22, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 3344, \"to\": 3420, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 3421, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"It wasn't something I intended to do [ignoring the handshake].\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Actually, I want to apologise to her and everyone else.\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3597, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was angry because my Olympics had gone up in smoke.\", \"from\": 3598, \"to\": 3651, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not have anything against Khelif.\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Actually, if I were to meet her again I would embrace her.\\\"\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3889, \"end\": 3902, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9290984724019034e-26, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3938, \"end\": 3951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9290984724019034e-26, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"